summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning, rezoning property bounded by 5th and 6th Avenues NE, NE Maple Leaf Place, NE 70th Street, and Interstate 5 from Lowrise 3 to Midrise 60 by amending the Official Land Use map, SMC Chapter 23.32, to implement the Green Lake Neighborhood Plan.
committee: Neighborhoods, Growth Planning and Civic Engagement
